## ğŸ“ Folder Structure

- `automation/` â€“ Python Selenium scripts for test automation  
- `mock-app/` â€“ Lightweight Flask app that simulates a real billing app  
- `test-cases/` â€“ Manual test documentation  
- `results/` â€“ Logs or output files from test runs  

